spec: asyncio_extra135
version: ">=3.9"
backend: python_module(asyncio)

docs: https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-sync.html

provenance:
  derived_from:
    - "https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio-sync.html — Python asyncio synchronization primitives documentation"
    - "Test vectors verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11"
  not_derived_from:
    - "CPython source: Lib/asyncio/locks.py"
  notes:
    - "This spec covers: wave 258 theme — asyncio.Condition method qualnames, lengths, and co_argcount. NEW in extra135: asyncio.Condition.__init__.__qualname__=='Condition.__init__' (len=18); asyncio.Condition.wait.__qualname__=='Condition.wait' (len=14); asyncio.Condition.notify.__qualname__=='Condition.notify' (len=16); asyncio.Condition.notify_all.__qualname__=='Condition.notify_all' (len=20); asyncio.Condition.wait_for.__qualname__=='Condition.wait_for' (len=18); asyncio.Condition.__module__=='asyncio.locks' (len=13); asyncio.Condition.__bases__[0].__name__=='_ContextManagerMixin'; asyncio.Condition.__mro__.__len__()==4; asyncio.Condition.__init__.__code__.co_argcount==2; asyncio.Condition.wait.__code__.co_argcount==1; asyncio.Condition.notify.__code__.co_argcount==2; asyncio.Condition.notify_all.__code__.co_argcount==1; asyncio.Condition.wait_for.__code__.co_argcount==2. All verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Condition does NOT have acquire or release as class-level attributes — those live on the lock passed to __init__. Condition.__init__ takes (self, lock) where lock defaults to None. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Condition.__mro__ == [Condition, _ContextManagerMixin, _LoopBoundMixin, object] (length=4). Same MRO depth as asyncio.Semaphore. Both Condition and Semaphore have _ContextManagerMixin as their first base. Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "asyncio.Condition.notify.__code__.co_argcount == 2 (self + n, where n defaults to 1). asyncio.Condition.notify_all.__code__.co_argcount == 1 (self only). asyncio.Condition.wait.__code__.co_argcount == 1 (self only). asyncio.Condition.wait_for.__code__.co_argcount == 2 (self + predicate). Verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
    - "All expected values verified with Python 3.14.3 on macOS/Darwin 25.4.0, 2026-04-11."
  created_at: "2026-04-11T00:00:00Z"

error_model: python_exceptions

